## Configuration Information
## Slot Information
### Configuration Keys
| Key      | Required | Type   | Description                                        |
|----------|----------|--------|----------------------------------------------------|
| pubId | true | String | The publisher id for this slot.                             |
| sizes    | true | Array<\[Number, Number]> | Sizes for this slot.
| dealId    | false | String | Deal id for this slot.

### Example
```json
 {
     "pubId": "386276e072",
     "sizes": [[300, 250]]
 }
```
